column5: hi guys im new to this forum and this is my first post! this site looked really cool and Ive seen some people that are also on other forums that i frequent. Now a little bit about me, im 14 and have been fishing since i was 5. I fly fish, pin, spin and baitcast, i mainly target, salmon, trout, bass, and pike, however i fish for just about anything if its there.My hobbies include a lot of making things, go karts, rc cars and planes and nerdy stuff lol. I hope to meet some of you guys on the water somethime  Cheers and tightlines-chasintails
ps. that pic was the only one i had small enough
